data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome to 2833 Shelburne Way, an impeccably maintained haven nestled in the desirable Gramercy Farms community. Boasting 4-bedrooms and 2 full baths, this residence is a testament to modern comfort and elegant design.      As you step into the home, the open floor plan seamlessly connects the living and dining rooms, creating a warm and inviting space for your family gatherings. The heart of the home lies in the spacious kitchen with a huge in-sink island, adorned with granite countertops, 42'' cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient pantry. The kitchen's charm is accentuated by matching decorative pendant lights and recessed lighting, bathing the entire area in a welcoming glow.      This residence is not just a home; it's an energy-efficient haven with ENERGY STAR #174 certification, low E windows, and 9'4'' ceilings. Extended ceramic tiles flow throughout the house, excluding the bedrooms, creating a stylish and low-maintenance living space.      The Master Suite, strategically located at the opposite end of the house, provides a tranquil retreat with added privacy. The Master Bath is a luxurious escape featuring dual marble sinks, an enclosed shower with custom tiles, and a delightful garden tub.      Step outside into the backyard oasis, where an open lanai beckons you to unwind. The (26' x 24') brick-paved extended patio and charming pergola set the stage for delightful outdoor gatherings with friends and family, all while enjoying the privacy of no rear neighbors.      Gramercy Farms offers more than just a home; it provides a community lifestyle with amenities such as playgrounds, a basketball court, a dog park, and a pavilion with picnic tables. The location is ideal, with close proximity to Lake Nona and Medical City, including the VA Hospital. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to Orlando International Airport, Melbourne Beach, the FL Turnpike, and US-192.      Experience the epitome of Florida living with the convenience of nearby shopping, restaurants, and entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to make 2833 Shelburne Way your new address, where luxury, comfort, and community converge seamlessly. Schedule your private tour today.
